Date:   Thu Jun 5 20:26:52 2014 +1000

    - BUG FIX: extfield was badly screwed up. Fixed it. There is also
    now a test-extfield.i test file, based on a sh6x6 with various extfield
    test cases.
    - BUG FIX: the display of the SHWFS spot pattern with the subapertures
    and area of interest, field stop, was also bad. It should now work.
    That's only when sim.debug>=1
    - BUG FIX: Again, bug related to extfield and rayleigh fixed (_nx4fft)
    - BUG FIX: a rare occurence bug could crash yao when command not defined
    when resetting. Fixed.
    - FEATURE: added flag wfs_disp_crop_edges, if set, enlarged edges due to
    extfield and spotpitch combination won't be displayed, providing a more
    natural look of the SHWFS spot image.
