commit 6faa5d9ad6b09bb647c928599d3adc461352d9d6
Author: Francois Rigaut <frigaut@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Oct 17 21:48:46 2012 +1100

    Got rid of power of 2 constraint in fftVE.
    - changed the API to _fftVE. third parameter is now dimension, not
    power of two such as 2^param = dimension. Can now compute FFT for
    any dimension. This function is supposed to be hidden as the
    exposed function is fftVE() which APIs have NOT changed.
    - fftVE() is now also named fftw()
    - bumped to 5.0.2

