commit 904f7a891823cf5e2faf4c5e9244d9ddb516cf40
Author: Francois Rigaut <frigaut@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Oct 16 12:36:06 2012 +1100

    Version 5.0.0:
    - Extensively tested version 4.10.99
    - import/export from wisdom file
    - statsokvec definition moved from aoinit to aoloop
    - added push4ttref (in arcsec) that can be defined for all wfs in parfile
    - fixed zero-day bug when loop.modalgainfile is not defined, that was
      producing and error difficult to understand/trace
    - added saving GxSP rco matrix in case allof(dm.fitvirtualdm==0) as it
      is needed anyway and will trigger a re-compute of the cmat.
    - cleaned up a bit yao.i to remove old comments and avoid long comments
      lines
    - fixed a bug introduce lately in which the simage was not embedded
      at the correct location in ximage when wfs._nx != wfs._nx4fft.
      _shwfs_phase2spots() API unchanged.
    - added generic sync_wfs() function. Although this might be in fact
      redondant with sync_wfs_forks()
    - changed the optimization of FFT dimension from exec time test to
      picking the first number for which the prime factors are all <= 7.
      The timing method was flawed as to get best results, one should
      optimize for all N values (or, less optimally, forget the optimization)
    - added/documented shwfs_comp_lgs_defocuses() and slope_offset_defocus(),
      convenience functions to set the lgs defocus and the slopes defocus
      offsets
    - added expand_path(), a fixed version of expand_file_name(), and
      prime_factors()

